{
  "stem": "26022.3",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And one of the largest halls in city hall had a desk at one end, and the rest was taken up with people standing in line who also had gotten their eviction notice.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And this man at the desk had a list of places where one could still push a few Jews in.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And, of course, at 4:00 or 5:00 or whenever he stopped, the line stopped, and these people had to come back the next day.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Now, this was a very scary thing because you really-- you never knew what are they going to follow up on and whatnot.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And one didn't want to take too many chances.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "So if they say, you should be out of there, maybe the Aryan tenant is coming in right then and there, and you're still there, and God knows what happens.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "On the other hand, they might never follow up, and they just have a vacancy, and it's there.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "So I don't know what would have happened if we had stayed there.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "But fortunately, we were still-- now, if you get out of line-- I hope you have no physical need to get out of line-- you can't ever get back.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You go to the end of the line again.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And some very bad things happened there, too.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "Well, anyhow, we were fortunate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "We got-- and then we got the ticket with the address, and Mama and I went there.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And that was that.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The house doesn't stand anymore.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "It got the full blast.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I mean, there is a house there now, but not-- not the original one.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "And so we were there for a couple of years.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Uh-huh, yeah.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    }
  ],
